00:20:43,988 --> 00:20:46,324
Cetak laporan kegiatan komite.

234
00:20:46,407 --> 00:20:47,742
Baik, Nn. Han.

235
00:20:49,076 --> 00:20:52,371
Pak Park. Tolong pantau wawancara pers
dan kelompok sipil.

236
00:20:52,455 --> 00:20:53,414
Baik.

237
00:20:57,084 --> 00:21:00,296
Halo. Saya Kim Mi-jin.
