Aku tak bisa memberi tahu rahasiaku.

714
00:49:30,046 --> 00:49:32,465
Jaga dirimu. Ayo.

715
00:49:33,049 --> 00:49:34,467
- Dah.
- Dah.

716
00:49:35,051 --> 00:49:37,428
